    "If the latter question was answered with \"yes\", participants could also indicate their exact profession.",
    "Finally, as an attention check, we asked participants who the stated source of the provided medical responses was (\"a licensed medical doctor\", \"an AI (Artificial Intelligence)-supported chatbot\", \"an AI (Artificial Intelligence)-supported chatbot, revised and supplemented by a licensed medical doctor\").",
    "We preregistered our analysis plan, data collection strategy, and the experimental design (https://osf.io/wn6mj).",
